    <sys:String x:Key="Wizard_Tip_ClickThroughBody" xmlns:sys="clr-namespace:System;assembly=mscorlib"> — Just click and drag the subtitle box to reposition it anywhere on screen. Press Ctrl+Shift+D to flash the dialogue area outline so you know where Kaption is looking.</sys:String>
